{
  "stem": "10698.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Lublin-- and we wound up all with them together into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the first death camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By then, we knew already that there is such thing as showers where you don't get water, but gas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People that did try to run-- to escape, and people started to know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where it's supposed to be at every of those death camps, they had a sign, Arbeit macht frei, meaning work makes free.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we undre-- first we had to undress in front of SS men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, SS men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stark naked, walking by, to go in into the shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we knew we were going for the sure death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went into a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we got some clothes that was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did you say to sister?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when we came out, we have to march again in front of the-- the-- the SS men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they decided who is going-- no, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They decided before we went to the shower who is going left or right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time we came out, we were getting different clothes, shoes that didn't match, and-- Was your hair shaved at the time?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not-- I never had my hair shaved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And would you believe that I had blonde curls once upon a time?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is my true color.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm bragging about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- so we came out, and we were taken to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We wound up with three more girls that we-- because each cot, whatever you call it--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bunk beds were taking five people at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were five people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
